00:36:32,300 --> 00:36:35,700
 nego mislim da kao stand-up komičar

421
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:36,940
 imam jedinstvenu priliku.

422
00:36:36,940 --> 00:36:38,460
 Dođu se ljudi tamo nasmijat,

423
00:36:38,460 --> 00:36:39,980
 platili su ulaznicu da se nasmiju,

424
00:36:39,980 --> 00:36:42,740
 stotine su oko njih ljudi

425
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:44,740
 i onda ja pričam,

426
00:36:44,740 --> 00:36:47,640
 pričam u svom najgorom danu,

427
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:48,940
 početak jednog šova,

428
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:51,800
