429
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:53,520
 gdje kažem da mu jednom,

430
00:36:53,620 --> 00:36:55,560
 u roku 12 sati mi je umro mentor,

431
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:58,200
 ostavila me cura i udario me auto.

432
00:36:58,200 --> 00:37:00,460
 I ljudi su kao šta?

433
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:02,720
 I ja ljudima kažem ono,

434
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:04,540
