436
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:08,620
 Ali nije, nije ubilo ljude.

437
00:37:08,620 --> 00:37:11,340
 Jer ja to krenem prič na taj način

438
00:37:11,340 --> 00:37:13,160
 i to sve da ljudi se smiju tome

439
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:14,820
