459
00:37:54,340 --> 00:37:56,320
 Ne, to je sad njih 300,

460
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,840
 ako ćemo po stocima,

461
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:58,740
 sad izmišlja malo,

462
00:37:58,740 --> 00:37:59,640
 ali recimo ono.

463
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:01,660
 I onda više nije jedan stol

464
00:38:01,660 --> 00:38:03,580
 koji su tu malo starije publike.

465
00:38:03,720 --> 00:38:04,840
 Ne, i njih je 400.

466
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,460
 Jer je Lisinski,

467
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:07,520
 jer je to ofensiv mjesto,

468
00:38:07,520 --> 00:38:08,260
 recimo to tako.

469
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:10,780
 I onda moraš imati tu bahatost,

470
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:12,360
 jer ako ti ne izađeš gore

471
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:13,340
 sa samopouzdanjem

472
00:38:13,340 --> 00:38:14,180
 da ti stvarno stojiš

473
00:38:14,180 --> 00:38:14,780
 iza te fore,

474
00:38:14,780 --> 00:38:15,820
 oni se neće nasmijat.

475
00:38:15,820 --> 00:38:18,940
 Sad dok pričaš,

476
00:38:18,940 --> 00:38:20,300
 otvara mi se milijardu pitanja.

477
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:25,420
 Da li u jedan smjer

478
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:26,260
 u kojem želim ići,

479
00:38:26,260 --> 00:38:31,420
 želim iz neke društvene prizme

480
00:38:31,420 --> 00:38:32,780
 ili konteksta društvenog nekog

481
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:34,020
 malo s pričastom

482
00:38:34,020 --> 00:38:36,340
 o stand-up komičarima,

483
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:38,980
 prvo sam te htio pitat

484
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:39,800
 šta misliš,

485
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:43,020
 koja je vaša uloga u društvu

486
00:38:43,020 --> 00:38:44,620
 i da li misliš da

487
00:38:44,620 --> 00:38:47,200
 iz vaše uloge se može napraviti

488
00:38:47,200 --> 00:38:48,680
 jako veliki utjecaj na društvo.

489
00:38:48,680 --> 00:38:51,860
 To je jedan smjer.

490
00:38:51,860 --> 00:38:53,260
 Drugo, čini mi se sad možda

491
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:55,120
 moje mišljenje

492
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:58,120
 da možda bi komičare

493
00:38:58,120 --> 00:38:58,940
 mogao,

